import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
def strategy(df):
    out = df.copy()
    out['ma5'] = out['close'].rolling(5).mean()
    out['ma20'] = out['close'].rolling(20).mean()
    out['signal'] = 0
    out.loc[out['ma5'] > out['ma20'], 'signal'] = 1
    out.loc[out['ma5'] <= out['ma20'], 'signal'] = -1
    out['signal'] = out['signal'].fillna(0)
    return out
